    <p>Pre­mieres on Dec 25 on Net­flix</p>
    <p>The lav­ish-look­ing Bridger­ton is the first Net­flix se­ries from Shon­da­land, the pro­duc­tion com­pany of tele­vi­sion hit maker and Grey’s Anatomy (2005 to present) cre­ator Shonda Rhimes.</p>
    <p>Cre­ated by her long-time col­lab­o­ra­tor Chris Van Dusen, this pe­riod piece, based on a se­ries of best-sell­ing ro­mance nov­els, fol­lows Daphne Bridger­ton (Phoebe Dynevor, Dick­en­sian, 2015 to 2016), el­dest daugh­ter of the Bridger­ton fam­ily. She makes her de­but in Re­gency Lon­don’s com­pet­i­tive mar­riage mar­ket, hop­ing to find a match rooted in true love.</p>

